<br>
What I find a bit sad is the dieing out of the lower zones for anyone over 60. Dinged 61 in Velks yesterday, immediately ALL spiders I conned were light blue. So much for a comfortable solo zone (even if exp was not great).<br>
<br>
I am just now going to explore the first set of planes, and looking forward to it. I guess there will be plenty of other people doing the same, so it wont be too bad getting a group.<br>
<br>
Soloing was nice, but I'm happy to group more again.<br>
Izudin<br>
