<br>
Tried chain casting pets.. Thats the best bet so far.  Takes a buttload of pets but you can take down 50-52 mobs pretty easy.<br>
<br>
Kiting is dangerous and very uncertain at best.  FoT is not a solve all for kiting.   Most of the Mobs take down the pets health so fast you'll end up having to resummon in the middle of a kite.  Which is nearly impossible to do.  (Unless you have some serious speed and quicksummoning level 3.)<br>
<br>
We can do some godly damage in PoP, but our soloing is very secondary compared to other classes.   Pulling out all the stops, using all our AA, and perhaps even some nice items we should be able to beat down a similar level of mob as a shaman could do at his best.<br>
